reviews.review_text: Excellent Sound I was trying to decide which copy of 11-05 was the crispiest and this one takes the cake.  Great sound, great show!

how about good lovin even a blind man knows when the sun is shining cause he can feel it feel it you can feel it too, RIGHT WAHT YOU GONNA Do.  I challenge you to find a better good lovin, anywhere, any year
The Eyes Have It! I concur with '74eyes that this is the toastiest. Great sound here, on my system at home anyway. A keeper/burner. Denon and Kirksaeters. A big, fat, fiver.
Best Looks Like Rain ever... What is DVDA? The details say the 24bit version is archived on DVDA?

LLR Awesome Looks like Rain, Can't entirely hear what bobby is saying at the end in the Grand Finally to this song where it explodes. i know he drops an F bomb. So much Passion...This song and BTW are my favorite tunes of his.
